
    ---------------------------------
	*  sfile (Search File)  README  *
    ---------------------------------

    WARNING /!\: Is a old program.
                 Maintained for compile on linux/macos.
                 Just fix bugs and add small options.

  - description:
  --------------
    Search file by name, inode, uid ... and search string in file.

  - Compilation:
  --------------
	(shell) $ tar zxvf sfile-x.x.x.tar.gz
	(shell) $ make

  - Compil for MacOS:
  -------------------
    (shell) $ MACOS=yes make

  - Installation:
  ---------------
	* copy bin file in dir: /usr/bin/
	(shell) $ make install

	Show help:
	----------
	(shell) $ sfile --help

  - Uninstall:
  ------------
    * delete bin /usr/bin/sfile
	(shell) $ make uninstall
